About Glatfelter—Beyond Paper®

Glatfelter on CNBC
Glatfelter Chairman and CEO Dante Parrini was featured on CNBC’s “Squawk 
	Box” prior to ringing the New York Stock Exchange closing bell with 
	Glatfelter senior leadership in April 2014. The televised event helped 
	celebrate Glatfelter’s 150th anniversary. 


	Watch the “Squawk Box” interview featuring Dante Parrini.
	
	A global supplier of specialty paper and engineered products, Glatfelter 
	delivers more than quality paper products. Going beyond paper is 
		our promise to our customers, based on over a century and a half of 
	experience and technical expertise and supported by new best-in-class 
	processes.
		

Glatfelter on Clear Channel
In celebration of Glatfelter’s 150th 
							anniversary, Chairman and CEO Dante Parrini was 
							interviewed by Michael Yorba on ‘The Trader’s 
							Network Show’. Listen to the 58 minute interview 
							here.  
            













Quality Products
Our products have expanded from 
							high-quality book publishing papers and envelopes to 
							an array of highly technical products like tea bags, 
							postage stamps, and playing cards. View our 
							product directory.















Innovative Approaches
Our people devise effective, creative 
							solutions to your paper challenges. Our process and 
							product innovations result from Glatfelter 
							People questioning the norm.















Customer Service With Global Reach
Our team approach to 
							customer service allows our experts to be your 
							dedicated resource. And with 
            locations in 
							North America, Europe and Asia, we have a global 
							presence to support you worldwide.















Sustainability
We conduct business using practices that 
							protect and enhance the 
							environmental, 
							social and 
							economic resources needed by future generations 
							to enjoy a life equal to or greater than our own.


 



			            
