Products > Nonwoven Wallcover Base    

	                    
Nonwoven Wallcover Base
Glatfelter is the leading global supplier of nonwoven wallcover base 
	materials. With vastly superior performance and functionality, nonwoven 
	wallcoverings are rapidly becoming the product of choice for installers and 
	design professionals around the world. Glatfelter nonwoven wallcover base is 
	recognized as the highest quality in this growing market.
Why Choose Glatfelter Nonwoven Wallcover Base Materials?






Superior performance
Dry strip-ability
Higher tear resistance
No material shrinkage or expansion when wet
Good runability for all modern processing methods
Quality Management System in accordance with ISO 9001:2008 and 
			ISO 14001:2004
FSC-certified product grades available



 
Select From These 
		Wallcover Base Materials:



65 gsm duplex nonwoven wallcover base, uncoated
130 - 150 gsm duplex nonwoven wallcover base, 
						uncoated
85 gsm duplex nonwoven wallcover base, coated
90 gsm duplex nonwoven wallcover base, coated
130 - 175 gsm duplex nonwoven wallcover base, coated



 

	The long tradition and high quality of Dresden wallpapers are now 
	incorporated into Glatfelter. Glatfelter’s wallcovering bases are filled 
	with the expertise and know-how for which Dresden is famous for. In April, 
	2013, Glatfelter acquired Dresden Papier. As Glatfelter Dresden, we will 
	continue to develop innovative products for years to come. 
	
		Thanks to our wide range of products, we can work with our customers to 
	develop tailor-made solutions. We are established leaders in creating 
	innovative 
		new product solutions, using many different materials, as well as in 
	customized product concepts. We also back up our nonwoven products with 
		superior customer service in every market we serve.  
	



			            
