Products > Food & Beverage Papers       

	                    
Food & Beverage Papers for Perfect Flavor and Aroma
As a global market leader, Glatfelter has built its reputation around 
	excellent customer service, consistent quality, and ongoing product 
	development. Whether you need tea bag papers, coffee filter papers, or food 
	casing papers, Glatfelter can provide a comprehensive range of off-the-shelf 
	products or custom designed solutions to meet your needs. 
Why Choose Glatfelter Food & Beverage Papers?






High quality filter papers with outstanding technical and 
				commercial support.
Excellent processing on fully automated packaging machines 
				at high converting speeds.
Innovative capabilities, unique solutions, and ongoing 
				product development support.
Global market leader in tea bag and coffee filter papers.
Wide range of personalization techniques including NELTEC, 
				WoW PRINTEC, and PERFOTEC, are available for branding and 
				product differentiation.



 
Select from these food & beverage papers:


		Coffee Filter Papers

		Tea Bag Papers

		Food Casing Papers



			Abaca Fiber












Glatfelter uses unique abaca fiber to 
							make our specialty food and beverage papers. Learn 
							more about this sustainable “super fiber.” 





			            
